			 Editions and supported features of SQL Server 2016 

					 
								 05/24/2017 
							 16 minutes to read 
							 
								 Contributors 
								 
											 
											 
											 
											 
								 

					 In this article 
						 THIS TOPIC APPLIES TO:   SQL Server (starting with 2016) Azure SQL Database Azure SQL Data Warehouse  Parallel Data Warehouse 
 This topic provides details of features supported by the SQL Server editions.  At this time there are no changes to features supported by editions for SQL Server 2017.   
 Installation requirements vary based on your application needs. The different editions of  SQL Server accommodate the unique performance, runtime, and price requirements of organizations and individuals. The  SQL Server components that you install also depend on your specific requirements. The following sections help you under